org.apache.catalina.util

类 ParameterMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.catalina.util.ParameterMap<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - The type of Key
    V - The type of Value
    所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Map<K,V>

    public final class ParameterMap<K,V>
extends Object
implements Map<K,V>, Serializable
    Implementation of java.util.Map that includes a locked property. This class can be used to safely expose Catalina internal parameter map objects to user classes without having to clone them in order to avoid modifications. When first created, a ParmaeterMap instance is not locked.
